ate\nphoto-consistent image manipulation that is otherwise very challenging to\nachieve.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Oct 2017 14:48:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 13 Nov 2017 15:40:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-15"}
